    <item>
      <title>美联储鲍威尔：利率峰值是否取决于数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-01/fed-s-powell-whether-rates-at-peak-will-depend-on-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔在新闻发布会上表示，在美联储政策制定联邦公开市场委员会决定将基准联邦基金利率的目标区间保留在5.25%至5.5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-01/fed-s-powell-whether-rates-at-peak-will-depend-on-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 19:34:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储主席鲍威尔暗示降息不会很快到来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-01/fed-chair-powell-signals-rate-cuts-aren-t-coming-soon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，他不知道美联储何时才能获得足够的信心开始降息。他是在美联储维持利率不变后发表上述言论的。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-01/fed-chair-powell-signals-rate-cuts-aren-t-coming-soon</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 19:33:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储主席鲍威尔暗示降息尚未结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-01/fed-chair-powell-signals-rate-cuts-are-not-close-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，通胀率仍然过高，无法保证在降低通胀率方面取得进一步进展。联邦公开市场委员会维持利率不变后，他在华盛顿发表了讲话。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-01/fed-chair-powell-signals-rate-cuts-are-not-close-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 19:19:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>维京 IPO 四月成为自九月以来美国上市表现最佳的月份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/viking-ipo-crowns-april-best-month-for-us-debuts-since-september</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国首次公开募股市场迎来了自 9 月份以来最大的一个月，交易范围不断扩大，激发了人们对复苏势头的乐观态度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/viking-ipo-crowns-april-best-month-for-us-debuts-since-september</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 19:13:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储的鹰派态度没有人们担心的那么强硬之后，美国国债扩大涨幅</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/treasuries-extend-gains-after-fed-less-hawkish-than-feared</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，目前的政策立场“足够限制”，并在通胀压力加大的情况下淡化了未来加息的可能性，导致美国两年期国债收益率大幅跌破5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/treasuries-extend-gains-after-fed-less-hawkish-than-feared</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 18:24:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储表示通胀缺乏进展，但暗示不太可能加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/fed-cites-lack-of-progress-on-inflation-holds-rates-steady</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储释放出对通胀的新担忧，同时表示可能会让借贷成本在较长时间内维持高位，而不是再次提高。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/fed-cites-lack-of-progress-on-inflation-holds-rates-steady</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 18:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>北美供应链因加拿大铁路罢工投票而受到威胁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/workers-gear-up-for-strike-against-two-canada-rail-giants</link>
      <description><![CDATA[要求增加休息时间的铁路工人接近罢工，罢工将扰乱从哈利法克斯到温哥华以及中西部到墨西哥湾的供应链。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/workers-gear-up-for-strike-against-two-canada-rail-giants</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 17:41:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国监管机构讨论最早于八月敲定银行资本规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/us-regulators-discuss-finalizing-bank-capital-rules-as-soon-as-august</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管一些批评人士呼吁放弃这一具有里程碑意义的计划，美联储和其他美国顶级监管机构仍在继续推进该计划，让大银行持有更多资本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/us-regulators-discuss-finalizing-bank-capital-rules-as-soon-as-august</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 16:20:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔淡化加息，股票和债券上涨：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在美联储的决定并不像华尔街担心的那样强硬之后，股市跟随债券上涨，杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示下一步不太可能加息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 22:37:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多斥资 250 亿美元的跨山输油管道扩建项目开始商业运营</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/trans-mountain-pipeline-gets-final-regulatory-clearance-to-ship-oil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[扩建后的跨山管道已进入商业运营，结束了加拿大最大、最具争议的能源项目之一长达十年的等待。]]></description>
